,'proj_caption','Gruppo Stelvio (formerly Bikeriders) is NYC’s online bike maintenance retailer, providing a highly edited product selection of parts and accessories that they deliver to your door and install.<br>\r\n<a href=\"http://stelvio.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Visit Site</a>\r\n\r\n'),(15899,534,'_proj_caption','field_53c59340a26cb'),(15900,534,'tb_single_0_lg_caption','BIKERIDERS NYC'),(15901,534,'_tb_single_0_lg_caption','field_55731b58e7ef2'),(15902,534,'tb_single_0_sm_caption','Shop & Book Online'),(15903,534,'_tb_single_0_sm_caption','field_55731bace7ef3'),(15904,534,'tb_single_0_color_capt','white'),(15905,534,'_tb_single_0_color_capt','field_557346250e17e'),(15906,534,'tb_single_0_bg_image','160'),(15907,534,'_tb_single_0_bg_image','field_5573199ff3bd1'),(15908,534,'tb_single_1_format','sq'),(15909,534,'_tb_single_1_format','field_54e3cfc482c32'),(15910,534,'tb_single_1_caption','Desktop Home Page \r\nSlider Animation\r\n'),(15911,534,'_tb_single_1_caption','field_55731bd6b9c66'),(15912,534,'tb_single_1_large_image','306'),(15913,534,'_tb_single_1_large_image','field_54e3d02382c33'),(15914,534,'tb_single_2_columns_text','1'),(15915,534,'_tb_single_2_columns_text','field_54e3cbc582c20'),(15916,534,'tb_single_2_text','<h1>Scrolling the Road</h1>\r\nI worked with the team at Bikeriders\r\nto create a seamless online experience for this one-of-a-kind Bike Shop.\r\nBuilt on Wordpress, we integrated a Third Party Online Scheduling called FullSlate to manage appointments with different Locations and/or Staff.\r\nFor the Shop, we used Lightspeed Webstore to integrate with their Point of Sale and synchronize their Inventory, Clients Database and Work Orders.\r\n\r\nThe UX Design approach was to serve one-page layouts, scrolling through a variation of color blocks and pictures to give the sensation of movement and speed as if the user were on the road... We also added some indicators on the bottom of each navigation items, sliding and following the cursor while animating the scroll to each sections.'),(15917,534,'_tb_single_2_text','field_54e3cc6482c21'),(15918,534,'tb_single_3_format','sq'),(15919,534,'_tb_single_3_format','field_54e3cfc482c32'),(15920,534,'tb_single_3_caption','About Page With\r\nScrolling Backgrounds'),(15921,534,'_tb_single_3_caption','field_55731bd6b9c66'),(15922,534,'tb_single_3_large_image','258'),(15923,534,'_tb_single_3_large_image','field_54e3d02382c33'),(15924,534,'tb_single_4_col_img','2'),(15925,534,'_tb_single_4_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(15926,534,'tb_single_4_pos_img','centered'),(15927,534,'_tb_single_4_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(15928,534,'tb_single_4_cap_img','Shop & Booking Pages'),(15929,534,'_tb_single_4_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(15930,534,'tb_single_4_image_1','139'),(15931,534,'_tb_single_4_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(15932,534,'tb_single_4_image_2','138'),(15933,534,'_tb_single_4_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(15934,534,'tb_single_5_col_img','3'),(15935,534,'_tb_single_5_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(15936,534,'tb_single_5_pos_img','centered'),(15937,534,'_tb_single_5_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(15938,534,'tb_single_5_cap_img','Smartphone Menu'),(15939,534,'_tb_single_5_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(15940,534,'tb_single_5_image_1','146'),(15941,534,'_tb_single_5_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(15942,534,'tb_single_5_image_2','141'),(15943,534,'_tb_single_5_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(15944,534,'tb_single_5_image_3','142'),(15945,534,'_tb_single_5_image_3','field_55a6a3916c1ff'),(15946,534,'tb_single','a:6:{i:0;s:16:\"background_image\";i:1;s:23:\"full_width_center_image\";i:2;s:11:\"description\";i:3;s:23:\"full_width_center_image\";i:4;s:7:\"row_img\";i:5;s:7:\"row_img\";}'),(15947,534,'_tb_single','field_54e3c95382c1c'),(15952,536,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/openingImage.jpg'),(15953,536,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:2560;s:6:\"height\";i:1920;s:4:\"file\";s:24:\"2015/09/openingImage.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbn