line platform that would facilitate remote sells.\r\n\r\nWe decided to built this with<a href=\"http://www.shopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Shopify</a>. Considering the price and rarity of most of the gallery items, we customize the check out process. Instead of the \'Add to Cart\', we created an Inquiry button; it creates a lead, build the clients database\r\nand keep the fantasy of the high end market intact.'),(17734,607,'_tb_single_3_text','field_54e3cc6482c21'),(17735,607,'tb_single_4_col_img','2'),(17736,607,'_tb_single_4_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(17737,607,'tb_single_4_pos_img','centered'),(17738,607,'_tb_single_4_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(17739,607,'tb_single_4_cap_img','Artist & Product Page'),(17740,607,'_tb_single_4_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(17741,607,'tb_single_4_image_1','546'),(17742,607,'_tb_single_4_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(17743,607,'tb_single_4_image_2','547'),(17744,607,'_tb_single_4_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(17745,607,'tb_single_5_vid','542'),(17746,607,'_tb_single_5_vid','field_56e853888db7b'),(17747,607,'tb_single_5_vid_2','543'),(17748,607,'_tb_single_5_vid_2','field_56ec0f2c0c177'),(17749,607,'tb_single_6_col_img','3'),(17750,607,'_tb_single_6_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(17751,607,'tb_single_6_pos_img','centered'),(17752,607,'_tb_single_6_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(17753,607,'tb_single_6_cap_img',''),(17754,607,'_tb_single_6_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(17755,607,'tb_single_6_image_1','548'),(17756,607,'_tb_single_6_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(17757,607,'tb_single_6_image_2','549'),(17758,607,'_tb_single_6_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(17759,607,'tb_single_6_image_3','550'),(17760,607,'_tb_single_6_image_3','field_55a6a3916c1ff'),(17761,607,'tb_single','a:7:{i:0;s:16:\"background_image\";i:1;s:23:\"full_width_center_image\";i:2;s:5:\"video\";i:3;s:11:\"description\";i:4;s:7:\"row_img\";i:5;s:5:\"video\";i:6;s:7:\"row_img\";}'),(17762,607,'_tb_single','field_54e3c95382c1c'),(17765,436