Director and Founder of Twenty First Gallery for many years now. He has engaged the needs of interior designers, collectors and private clients with his gift for sourcing treasures. His challenge, though has allways been to bring people to visit the gallery space in chelsea, we needed an online platform that would facilitate remote sells.\r\n\r\nWe decided to built this with<a href=\"http://www.shopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Shopify</a>. Considering the price and rarity of most of the gallery items, we customize the check out process. Instead of the \'Add to Cart\', we created an Inquiry button; it creates a lead, build the clients database\r\nand keep the fantasy of the high end market intact.'),(22072,752,'_tb_single_3_text','field_54e3cc6482c21'),(22073,752,'tb_single_4_col_img','2'),(22074,752,'_tb_single_4_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(22075,752,'tb_single_4_pos_img','centered'),(22076,752,'_tb_single_4_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(22077,752,'tb_single_4_cap_img','Artist & Product Page'),(22078,752,'_tb_single_4_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(22079,752,'tb_single_4_image_1','546'),(22080,752,'_tb_single_4_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(22081,752,'tb_single_4_image_2','547'),(22082,752,'_tb_single_4_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(22083,752,'tb_single_5_vid','542'),(22084,752,'_tb_single_5_vid','field_56e853888db7b'),(22085,752,'tb_single_5_vid_2','543'),(22086,752,'_tb_single_5_vid_2','field_56ec0f2c0c177'),(22087,752,'tb_single_6_col_img','3'),(22088,752,'_tb_single_6_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(22089,752,'tb_single_6_pos_img','centered'),(22090,752,'_tb_single_6_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(22091,752,'tb_single_6_cap_img',''),(22092,752,'_tb_single_6_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(22093,752,'tb_single_6_image_1','548'),(22094,752,'_tb_single_6_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(22095,752,'tb_single_6_image_2','549'),(22096,752,'_tb_single_6_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(22097,752,'tb_single_6_image_3','550'),(22098,752,'_tb_single_6