'field_55a530d1c2e6a'),(27658,954,'tb_single_3_columns_text','1'),(27659,954,'_tb_single_3_columns_text','field_54e3cbc582c20'),(27660,954,'tb_single_3_text','<h1>Scrolling the Road</h1>\r\nI worked with the team at Bikeriders\r\nto create a seamless online experience for this one-of-a-kind Bike Shop.\r\nBuilt on Wordpress, we integrated a Third Party Online Scheduling called FullSlate to manage appointments with different Locations and/or Staff.\r\nFor the Shop, we used Lightspeed Webstore to integrate with their Point of Sale and synchronize their Inventory, Clients Database and Work Orders.\r\n\r\nThe UX Design approach was to serve one-page layouts,\r\nscrolling through a variation of blocks and pictures to give the sensation of movement and speed as if the user were on the road...\r\nWe also added some indicators on the bottom of each navigation items, sliding and following the cursor while it animates the scroll to each sections.'),(27661,954,'_tb_single_3_text','field_54e3cc6482c21'),(27662,954,'tb_single_4_format','sq'),(27663,954,'_tb_single_4_format','field_54e3cfc482c32'),(27664,954,'tb_single_4_caption','About Page With\r\nScrolling Backgrounds'),(27665,954,'_tb_single_4_caption','field_55731f52326e9'),(27666,954,'tb_single_4_large_image','149'),(27667,954,'_tb_single_4_large_image','field_54e3d02382c33'),(27668,954,'tb_single_5_row_images_0_columns_img','3'),(27669,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images_0_columns_img','field_54e3cb6182c1d'),(27670,954,'tb_single_5_row_images_0_pos_img','centered'),(27671,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images_0_pos_img','field_55a530d1c2e6a'),(27672,954,'tb_single_5_row_images_0_img1_cap','Smartphone Menu'),(27673,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images_0_img1_cap','field_55731f70326ea'),(27674,954,'tb_single_5_row_images_0_image_1','146'),(27675,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images_0_image_1','field_54e3cb7e82c1e'),(27676,954,'tb_single_5_row_images_0_image_2','141'),(27677,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images_0_image_2','field_54e3cd2882c28'),(27678,954,'tb_single_5_row_images_0_image_3','142'),(27679,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images_0_image_3','field_54e3cf2182c2a'),(27680,954,'tb_single_5_row_images','1'),(27681,954,'_tb_single_5_row_images','field_54e4cfc1ff995'),(27682,954,'tb_single_2_columns_text','1'),(27683,954,'_tb_single_2_columns_text','field_54e3cbc582c20'),(27684,954,'tb_single_2_text','<h1>Scrolling the Road</h1>\r\nI worked with the team at Bikeriders to create a seamless online experience for this one-of-a-kind Bike Shop. Built on Wordpress, we integrated a Third Party Online Scheduling to manage appointments with different Locations and/or Staff. For the Shop, we used Shopify to integrate with their Point of Sale and synchronize their Inventory, Clients Database and Work Orders.\r\n\r\nThe UX Design approach was to serve one-page layouts, scrolling through a variety of color blocks and pictures to give the sensation of movement and speed as if the user were on the road... We also added some indicators on the bottom of each navigation items, sliding and following the cursor while animating the scroll to each section.'),(27685,954,'_tb_single_2_text','field_54e3cc6482c21'),(27686,954,'tb_single_4_col_img','2'),(27687,954,'_tb_single_4_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(27688,954,'tb_single_4_pos_img','centered'),(27689,954,'_tb_single_4_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(27690,954,'tb_single_4_cap_img','Shop & Booking Pages'),(27691,954,'_tb_single_4_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(27692,954,'tb_single_4_image_1','139'),(27693,954,'_tb_single_4_image_1','field_55a6a3916c1fd'),(27694,954,'tb_single_4_image_2','138'),(27695,954,'_tb_single_4_image_2','field_55a6a3916c1fe'),(27696,954,'tb_single_5_col_img','3'),(27697,954,'_tb_single_5_col_img','field_55a6a3916c1fa'),(27698,954,'tb_single_5_pos_img','centered'),(27699,954,'_tb_single_5_pos_img','field_55a6a3916c1fb'),(27700,954,'tb_single_5_cap_img','Smartphone Menu'),(27701,954,'_tb_single_5_cap_img','field_55a6a3916c1fc'),(27702,954,'tb_single_5_image_1','146'),(27703